{"tid":1078200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連續兩日  瀑布灣公園上吊亡","createTime":"2019-03-26T06:38:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T07:15:30.000Z","uid":30647,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f9d6bf3e282cc52853d660f1c5ecbbd272f42bf7","tid":1078200,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:38:03.000Z","msg":"連續兩日 瀑布灣公園 都有吊頸自殺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3月25日 星期一<br />\n今日（25日）清晨6時21分，途人路經香港仔瀑布灣公園，發現一名男子在長櫈上蓋以尼龍繩自縊，大驚報警。警方及消防趕至現場將男子救下，惟證實已經死亡。警員到場調查，證實死者為一名姓黃(33歲)男子，並在現場檢獲遺書。據了解，事主疑受疾病困擾。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190325/bkn-20190325063227456-0325_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190325%2Fbkn-20190325063227456-0325_00822_001.html&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=e420f405\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190325/bkn-20190325063227456-0325_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n3月26日 今日<br />\n香港仔華富邨瀑布灣公園，中午近12時，一名男子被發現在樹上吊頸自殺，救護員接報到場，證實男子當場死亡。現場消息稱，62歲事主早前由家人報失，為一名失蹤人士<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190326/59413216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59413216&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=e40c4159\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59413216&h=2099e144\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190326/59413216</a>"},{"pid":"bc9ec7f3f4a66d79d12910bf0268b251bb7659a6","tid":1078200,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:38:58.000Z","msg":"62歲事主早前由家人報失<br />\n<br />\n銀包呀 報失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c878e9b1c812e11b5f1f1dc850ae8b4eae976d","tid":1078200,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:39:14.000Z","msg":"自殺勝地"},{"pid":"ce615d62c1fcbb52655522a7304e5bb9e7d4ba76","tid":1078200,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n落到去玩hehe"},{"pid":"2977e12c3bc0f9f35a9f35538e611dee2749674b","tid":1078200,"uid":112448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:40:45.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"31f36f5895585bcfc45ffebd707c5eb5e468c090","tid":1078200,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:41:00.000Z","msg":"香港樹海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c46095866b0663c47ed5649f623c83a00f9222e","tid":1078200,"uid":35014,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9205fa9b6c3de7efe79307c46f70b1d6bc92ab9f","tid":1078200,"uid":50386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:48:01.000Z","msg":"香港版青木原樹海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407a2030e7112aa73a9cb04ff5c636e8a87a2361","tid":1078200,"uid":196582,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:58:59.000Z","msg":"瀑布灣不嬲都好猛 咩搵替死鬼嗰啲成日都聽"},{"pid":"4dac8e9e67fcd19ed87c5c283401ffa361b98f68","tid":1078200,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:59:10.000Z","msg":"聽日會唔會&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e6508d03662f41ec03971ecd11fd5255260f4d","tid":1078200,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:00:09.000Z","msg":"要送肉棕"},{"pid":"549a042b2a879143c82aa8bfd92229ede5fdb4d7","tid":1078200,"ui